ision ===\n==== Drama ====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Network\n!Notes\n!Ref.\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[The Sound of Your Heart (TV series)|The Sound of Your Heart]]''\n|Neighbor in Apt. 205\n|[[Naver|Naver TV Cast]]<br />[[KBS2]]\n|Special appearance\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[School 2017]]''\n|Ra Eun-ho\n|[[KBS2]]\n|Lead role \n|<ref name=\"school2017\" />\n|-\n|2019\n|[[I Wanna Hear Your Song|''I Wanna Hear Your Song'']]\n|Hong Yi-young\n|[[KBS2]]\n|Lead role\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=469&aid=0000379964|title=\uc5f0\uc6b0\uc9c4X\uae40\uc138\uc815X\uc1a1\uc7ac\ub9bcX\ubc15\uc9c0\uc5f0, KBS2 \u2018\ub108\uc758 \ub178\ub798\ub97c \ub4e4\ub824\uc918\u2019 \uce90\uc2a4\ud305 [\uacf5\uc2dd]|last=|first=|date=April 12, 2019|website=Naver|language=ko|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=April 7, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n====Variety show====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Network\n! Note / Role\n!Ref.\n|-\n| 2012\u20132013\n| ''[[K-pop Star 2]]''\n| [[Seoul Broadcasting System|SBS]]\n| Eliminated in casting audition round\n|<ref name=\"kpopstar2\" /><ref name=\"kpopstar3\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2016\n| ''[[Produce 101]]''\n| rowspan=\"1\" |[[Mnet (TV channel)|Mnet]]\n| Survival show that determined I.O.I members\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Talents for Sale]]''\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[KBS2]]\n| Regular host\n|<ref name=talents />\n|-\n| ''Boom Shakalaka''\n| Contestant\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Immortal Songs: Singing the Legend|Immortal Songs 2]]''\n| Contestant (Episode 282)\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2017\n| ''[[1 vs 100]]''\n| Contestant (Episode 466)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[King of Mask Singer]]''\n| [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n| Contestant as \"Worker Holic Antgirl\" (Episode 95)\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2017012217134598446|title='\ubcf5\uba74\uac00\uc655' \ub300\uc138 \uc18c\ub140 \uae40\uc138\uc815, \ub5a0\ub098 \ubcf4\ub0b4\uae30 \uc544\uae4c\uc6b4 \ucd5c\uac15 \uac00\ucc3d\ub825|author=Song Yoon-jeong|date=January 22, 2017|work=Asia Economic Daily|accessdate=January 22, 2017|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Law of the Jungle (TV series)#Sumatra|Law of the Jungle in Sumatra]]''\n| [[Seoul Broadcasting System|SBS]]\n| Cast member\n|<ref name=\"kpopherald1\">{{cite news|url=http://kpopherald.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=201701161453361611955_2|title=Gugudan's Sejeong joins 'Law of the Jungle'|author=Jie Ye-eun|date=January 16, 2017|accessdate=February 28, 2017|website=Kpop Herald}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://stoo.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2017011609171905386|title=\uad6c\uad6c\ub2e8 \uae40\uc138\uc815 '\uc815\uae00\uc758 \ubc95\uce59' \uccab \ucd9c\uc5f0, \uc778\ub3c4\ub124\uc2dc\uc544 \ucd9c\uad6d|author=Kim Eun-ae|date=January 16, 2017|work=Sports Today|accessdate=February 2, 2017|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Get It Beauty''\n| [[OnStyle]]\n| Regular host \n|<ref name=\"hostGIB\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kpopherald.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=201707091527214118198_2|title=Kim Se-jeong to leave 'Get It Beauty': report|date=July 9, 2017|work=Kpop Herald}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Battle Trip]]''\n|[[KBS2]]\n| Contestant with Nayoung (Episode 40\u201341) <br>Special Host (Episode 48\u201349)\n|<ref>{{cite web|title= Gugudan's Kim Sejeong To Take on Role As Special MC For \"Battle Trip\"|url=https://www.soompi.com/2017/04/27/gugudans-kim-sejeong-take-role-special-mc-battle-trip/|website=Soompi|accessdate=21 August 2017|date=27 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=\uae40\uc138\uc815, '\ubc30\ud2c0\ud2b8\ub9bd' \uc2a4\ud398\uc15c MC \ubc1c\ud0c1\u20252\uc8fc\uac04 \ud65c\uc57d \uc608\uc815|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=112&aid=0002915320|website=NAVER|accessdate=21 August 2017|language=Korean|date=28 April 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2018\n| ''[[Baek Jong-won's Alley Restaurant]]''\n| [[Seoul Broadcasting System|SBS]]\n| Special co-host (Episodes 1\u201310)\n|<ref>{{Cite news|author=Park Seul-gi|title=['\uace8\ubaa9\uc2dd\ub2f9'\uccab\ubc29] \ubc31\uc885\uc6d0\uc758 \ubcf8\uaca9 \uace8\ubaa9 \uc0c1\uad8c \uc0b4\ub9ac\uae30(feat.\uac15\ub825\ud574\uc9c4 \ub3c5\uc124)|url=http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/1389643|work=TenAsia|date=January 6, 2018|accessdate=March 23, 2018|language=ko}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Son Jae-eun|title=[\uc2a4\ube0c\uc2a4\u591c] \uace8\ubaa9\uc2dd\ub2f9 \uae40\uc138\uc815, \ubc31\uc885\uc6d0 \uc8fc\ub2c8\uc5b4\uc758 \ud65c\uc57d (feat \uace0\uc7ac\uadfc \ub0a8\ucc3d\ud76c)|url=https://news.sbs.co.kr/news/endPage.do?news_id=N1004561311|work=SBS News|date=January 6, 2018|accessdate=March 23, 2018|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Galileo: Awakened Universe''\n| [[tvN]]\n| Cast member\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.sbs.co.kr/news/endPage.do?news_id=N1004752369&plink=SEARCH&cooper=SBSNEWSSEARCH|title=[SBS Star] gugudan SEJEONG to Explore Mars with Kim Byung-man!|date=May 10, 2018|website=SBS News}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Happy Together (talk show)|Happy Together 4]]\n|[[KBS Entertainment Awards|KBS]]\n|Special MC\n|\n|-\n| 2018\u2013present\n| ''[[Busted!]]''\n| [[Netflix]]\n| Cast member; 2 seasons \n|<ref name=busted />\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[King of Mask Singer]]''\n|[[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n|Contestant as \"Eliza\" (Episodes 197\u2013198)\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=112&aid=0003150887|title='\ubcf5\uba74\uac00\uc655' \uc774\ub77c\uc774\uc790 \uc815\uccb4\ub294 \uad6c\uad6c\ub2e8 \uae40\uc138\uc815, \"\ubb34\ub300 \uc704\uc5d0\uc11c \uc138 \ubc88 \uc6b8\uc5c8\ub2e4\"(\uc885\ud569)|last=|first=|date=April 7, 2019|website=Naver|language=ko|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{see also|List of awards and nominations received by I.O.I|Gugudan#Awards and nominations}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category\n!Nominated work\n!Result\n!Ref.\n|-\n|2016\n| 15th [[KBS Entertainment Awards]]\n| Rookie Variety\n|