per League]]\n|-\n|[[ASEB SC]]||[[Guwahati]]||align=\"center\"|GSA Super Division League\n|-\n|Navajyoti FC||[[Guwahati]]||align=\"center\"|GSA Super Division League\n|-\n|Assam Police Blues||[[Guwahati]]||align=\"center\"|GSA Super Division League\n|-\n|NFR SC||[[Guwahati]]||align=\"center\"|GSA Super Division League\n|-\n|[[Gauhati Town Club]]||[[Guwahati]]||align=\"center\"|GSA A Division League\n|-\n|[[Guwahati City FC]]||[[Guwahati]]||align=\"center\"|GSA C Division League\n|-\n|Assam Rifles SC||[[Tezpur]]||align=\"center\"|-\n|-\n|[[Oil India Ltd FC]]||[[Duliajan]]||align=\"center\"|-\n|-\n|SAI SC||[[Kokrajhar]]||align=\"center\"|-\n|}\n\n===Bihar===\n''Main State League: ''Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n!!width=\"25%\"|Club!!width=\"30%\"|Town or City!!width=\"45%\"|League\n|-\n|[[Shirsh Bihar United Football Club (Patna)|Shirsh Bihar United Football Club]]\n|[[Patna]]\n|align=\"center\"|[[I-League 2nd Division]]\n|-\n|[[Rainbow Football Club (Patna)|Rainbow Football Club]]\n|[[Patna]]\n|align=\"center\"|Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n|-\n|[[Sporting Football Club (Patna)|Sporting Football Club]]\n|[[Patna]]\n|align=\"center\"|Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n|-\n| [[Friends Football Club (Patna)|Friends Football Club]]\n|[[Patna]]\n|align=\"center\"|Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n|-\n| [[Rajmilk Football Club (Patna)|Rajmilk Football Club]]\n|[[Patna]]\n|align=\"center\"|Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n|-\n| [[RK Steel (Siwan)|RK Steel]]\n|[[Siwan, Bihar|Siwan]]\n|align=\"center\"|Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n|-\n| [[Adivasi United (Purnea)|Adivasi United]]\n|[[Purnea]]\n|align=\"center\"|Moin-ul-Haq Cup\n|}\n\n===Delhi===\n''Main State League: [[Delhi Senior Division]]''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n!!width=\"25%\"|Club!!width=\"30%\"|Town or City!!width=\"45%\"|League\n|-\n|[[Delhi F.C.|Delhi]]||[[New Delhi]] and [[Uttarakhand]]||align=\"center\"|[[Delhi Senior Division]]\n|-\n|[[Delhi United S.C.|Delhi United]]||[[New Delhi]] and [[Greater Noida]]||align=\"cen