ice]]||[[Jalandhar]]||align=\"center\"|-\n|-\n|[[United Punjab FC]]||[[Pathankot]]||align=\"center\"|-\n|}\n\n===Rajasthan===\n''Main State League: [[RAJASTHAN League]]''\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n!!width=\"25%\"|Club!!width=\"30%\"|Town or City!!width=\"45%\"|League\n|-\n|[[Rajasthan F.C.|AU Rajasthan]]||[[Rajasthan]]||align=\"center\"|[[I-League 2nd division]]\n|-\n|[[MEWAR F.C.|MEWAR]]||[[MEWAR]]||align=\"center\"|[[RAJASTHAN LEAGUE]]\n|-\n|[[NEERJA MODI F.C.|NMFA]]||[[Jaipur]]||align=\"center\"|[[RAJASTHAN LEAGUE]]\n|-\n|[[PLAYSPACE F.C.|PLAYSPACE]]||[[Jaipur]]||align=\"center\"|[[RAJASTHAN LEAGUE]]\n|-\n|[[ZINC F.C.|ZINC ACADEMY]]||[[UDAIPUR]]||align=\"center\"|[[RAJASTHAN LEAGUE]]\n|-\n\n===Sikkim===\n''Main State League: [[Sikkim Senior Division]]''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n!!width=\"25%\"|Club!!width=\"30%\"|Town or City!!width=\"45%\"|League\n|-\n|[[Sikkim F.C.]]||[[Gangtok]]||align=\"center\"|[[I-League]]\n|-\n|[[Gangtok Himalayan S.C.]]||[[Gangtok]]||align=\"center\"|[[I-League 2nd Division]]\n|-\n|[[United Sikkim F.C.|United Sikkim]]||[[Gangtok]]||align=\"center\"|[[I-League 2nd Division]]\n|-\n|[[Denzong Boys FC]]||[[Gangtok]]||align=\"center\"|-\n|}\n\n===Tamil Nadu===\n''Main State League: [[Chennai Football Senior Division]]''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n!!width=\"25%\"|Club!!width=\"30%\"|Town or City!!width=\"45%\"|League\n|-\n|[[Chennai City F.C.]]||[[Coimbatore]]||align=\"center\"|[[I-League]]\n|-\n| [[Indian Bank Recreational Club|Indian Bank Sports & R.C.]]||[[Chennai]]||align=\"center\"|[[Chennai Football Senior Division]]\n|-\n|[[Viva Chennai F.C.]]||[[Chennai]]||align=\"center\"|[[I-League 2nd Division]]\n|-\n|[[Hindustan Eagles F.C.]]||[[Chennai]]||align=\"center\"|[[Chennai Football Senior Division]]\n|-\n|[[Chennai United F.C]]||[[Chennai]]||align=\"center\"|[[Chennai Football Senior Division]]\n|-\n|[[Chennai F.C.]]||[[Chennai]]||align=\"center\"|[[Chenna